# Evidence pulled back by run-remote.sh: timestamped dmesg/sysfs/procfs
# dumps from the tablet. Treated as disposable/regenerable working data,
# not a permanent record — re-running the session produces a fresh
# directory every time and these can add up (full dmesg dumps etc).
#
# The permanent record of a session's results belongs in
# docs/HARDWARE_TEST_MATRIX.md (per-row pass/fail + a reference to the
# evidence path/date), not in committed raw captures here. If a specific
# capture needs to be preserved long-term, copy it out explicitly (e.g.
# into baseline/ or an attached artifact) rather than un-ignoring this.
evidence/*
!evidence/.gitkeep
